Spec §3 still references `scripts/vps-bootstrap/provision-credentials.sh` (line 575). Plan 01a (merged `20c8348`) ships `runtime/deploy/provision-credentials.sh`. Both `rotate-telegram-bot.sh:67` and `02-telegram-bot-rotation.md:54` correctly use `runtime/deploy/` — translation applied ✓. Spec text still has stale path (separate amendment ticket).

## NDJSON shape consistency with spec §10 criterion 5

Both scripts emit `{"ts","script","step","status","detail"}` with consistent schema. Status enum: `ok`, `fail`, `pending` (rotate retry). `script` field disambiguates source. `detail` is JSON-encoded via `jq -Rs` — single line per record ✓.

